IMPACT OF A POTENTIAL PRODUCTION SHUT-DOWN, INCLUDING ANY RECOVERY THAT WOULD BE AVAILABLE FROM THE U.S. GOVERNMENT. SUCH RECOVERY FROM THE U.S. GOVERNMENT WOULD NOT INCLUDE THE COSTS INCURRED BY

